# Ankabut Radio

## Icon
![icon](http://ankabut-radio.googlecode.com/git/res/drawable-xhdpi/ic_launcher.png)

## Descriptions
This is the backup repositories for Ankabut Radio from http://code.google.com/p/ankabut-radio/
For more detail, signed APK and Wikis, please refer to [Ankabut @Google Project](http://code.google.com/p/ankabut-radio/).

## Signed APK Download
We currently doesn't have Google Play account to publish our APK because of registration issue. Instead using google play, you can download the APK file from google project hosting in this [link](http://code.google.com/p/ankabut-radio/downloads/list).

***
### Authors and Contributors
Author: @baka-hayi as Lead developer (solo fighter). :p

### Support or Contact
This project is just begun. And we really need your support to make this project getting better and meet the users expectations. We appreciate yous comments and suggestion. For more information about this project just mail me at teloquitous[at]gmail.com.
